Simple console widget based on libkonsolepart.

It requires kdelibs, Konsole, PyKDE from KDE 4.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ver 0.3: [2012-09-20]
- Transparency and popup.

ver 0.2.3: [2009-09-14]
- Fixed reset of height and width values after reboot/relogin/readd.

ver 0.2.2: [2009-08-23]
- Issue with closing session in "no tab" mode fixed.

ver 0.2.1: [2009-08-21]
- Some fixes and changes with opening new sessons.
- Now the last one session is restared after closing.

ver 0.2: [2009-07-31]
- Added tabs support. Fixed some issues.

ver 0.1.1: [2009-07-14]
- Now plasmoid is deleted when session is closed.

ver 0.1: [2009-07-08]                                                                              
- Basic functionality - it simply loads libkonsolepart.so :-).
- Plasmacon works normally only in KDE 4.3 at this moment.                                                                     

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Developed on Gentoo with Python 2.7.3 on KDE 4.9.0
